"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/evaluation-reliability/regression-gates#5-常见反模式","content":"只看一次通过，不追踪发布后漂移；"},"218":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/evaluation-reliability/regression-gates-18","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/evaluation-reliability/regression-gates","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/evaluation-reliability/regression-gates#5-常见反模式","content":"例外开口太大，最终门禁失效。"},"219":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking","type":"page","content":"Embedding 与切块策略","breadcrumbs":["Docs","Introduction","AI Engineering","Foundations"],"tags":[],"url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking"},"220":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking-0","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking","content":"向量召回质量与 Chunking 策略的设计要点。"},"221":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking-1","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking#1-问题定义","content":"1) 问题定义"},"222":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking-2","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking#2-chunking-设计原则","content":"2) Chunking 设计原则"},"223":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking-3","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking#3-embedding-选型与索引要点","content":"3) Embedding 选型与索引要点"},"224":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking-4","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking#4-评估指标建议同时看离线与在线","content":"4) 评估指标（建议同时看离线与在线）"},"225":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking-5","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking#5-常见失败模式","content":"5) 常见失败模式"},"226":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking-6","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking#6-落地建议","content":"6) 落地建议"},"227":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking-7","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking#1-问题定义","content":"Embedding 与 Chunking 的目标不是“把文档切碎”，而是让检索系统能稳定找回可回答问题的证据单元。检索质量差时，继续调 Prompt 往往只能掩盖问题，不能解决问题。"},"228":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking-8","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking#2-chunking-设计原则","content":"语义完整优先：按标题、段落、步骤、表格边界切分；"},"229":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking-9","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking#2-chunking-设计原则","content":"单块单主题：一个 chunk 最好只服务一个检索意图；"},"230":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking-10","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking#2-chunking-设计原则","content":"适度重叠：降低边界信息断裂，避免答案“差最后一句”；"},"231":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking-11","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking#2-chunking-设计原则","content":"元数据外置：来源、版本、更新时间、权限标签要结构化存储。"},"232":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking-12","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking#3-embedding-选型与索引要点","content":"模型选型优先看领域匹配，而不是只看通用榜单分数；"},"233":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking-13","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking#3-embedding-选型与索引要点","content":"索引设计要考虑过滤条件（租户、权限、时间）；"},"234":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking-14","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking#3-embedding-选型与索引要点","content":"混合检索（关键词 + 向量）通常比纯向量更稳健；"},"235":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking-15","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking#3-embedding-选型与索引要点","content":"重排（rerank）应聚焦“前 k 条质量”，而非全量排序精度。"},"236":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking-16","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking#4-评估指标建议同时看离线与在线","content":"命中率（Hit@k）：正确证据是否进入候选集合；"},"237":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking-17","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking#4-评估指标建议同时看离线与在线","content":"覆盖率（Coverage）：复杂问题所需证据是否齐全；"},"238":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking-18","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking#4-评估指标建议同时看离线与在线","content":"噪声率（Noise）：无关 chunk 占比是否过高；"},"239":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking-19","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking#4-评估指标建议同时看离线与在线","content":"证据密度：最终输入给模型的上下文中有效信息占比。"},"240":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking-20","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking#5-常见失败模式","content":"按固定字符切块：跨段断裂，关键前提和结论被拆开；"},"241":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking-21","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking#5-常见失败模式","content":"元数据缺失：召回出来但无法过滤过期或低可信来源；"},"242":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking-22","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking#5-常见失败模式","content":"只做向量检索：对精确术语、配置项、错误码召回不稳定。"},"243":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking-23","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking#6-落地建议","content":"先用 50~100 个真实问题做离线标注集；"},"244":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking-24","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking#6-落地建议","content":"每次只改一个变量（切块大小、重叠、检索 k、重排模型）；"},"245":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking-25","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking#6-落地建议",